<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <title>Content Delivery from Beefree</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f8;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 5px solid #bdc3c7; /* Colore neutro (grigio) */
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }
        hr {
            border: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: #eee;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .abuse-section {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>SDKMedia Content Delivery Network</h1>
    <p>This infrastructure provides high-availability asset hosting for the <strong>BeeFree</strong> ecosystem.</p>
    
    <p>Services hosted here include static images, stylesheets, and fonts used in email design and digital communication.</p>

    <hr>

    <div class="abuse-section">
        <p>Managed by Bee content design inc. Registered Office:  San Francisco, CA.</p>
        <p>For technical documentation, inquiries or to report abuse use <a href="https://policy.sdkmedia.net/abuse">this link</a></p>
        <p><a href="https://policy.sdkmedia.net/gdpr-compliance">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="https://policy.sdkmedia.net/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>